{"tid":1326197,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［前一大］警員凌晨闖入港大校園　港大將向警方投訴","createTime":"2019-07-17T06:34:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T06:34:09.000Z","uid":76508,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"67e20e63cfc90f98b49138174001838e72fb8fc0","tid":1326197,"uid":76508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:34:09.000Z","msg":"6.12 金鐘大規模警民衝突後，一度傳出警方到港大宿舍搜捕，港大學生早前和校長張翔對話，張翔當時承諾，如無搜查令不會讓警方進入校園。港大今日發聲明，指凌晨有警員進入港大校園，逗留了幾分鐘，校方非常關注。<br />\n<br />\n聲明又指，大學保安當時即時向警方查詢，爲何有警務人員違反既定守則進入校園範圍，港大會向警方正式投訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/警員凌晨闖入港大校園-港大將向警方投訴/#.XS60nkNvWhc.facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%87%8C%E6%99%A8%E9%97%96%E5%85%A5%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%A0%A1%E5%9C%92-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%87%E5%90%91%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%2F%23.XS60nkNvWhc.facebook&d=SosmRuku1xQpFtIKZJ5auVxDM7DnHmdvX2f5RcY9ddA%3D&h=7194342e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%87%8C%E6%99%A8%E9%97%96%E5%85%A5%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%A0%A1%E5%9C%92-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%87%E5%90%91%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%2F%23.XS60nkNvWhc.facebook&h=ae99743c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/警員凌晨闖入港大校園-港大將向警方投訴/#.XS60nkNvWhc.facebook</a>"}]}